## Kuti mwatila amuti ni mucilooto ifyo uyu mulumemdo aishilecita ilyo afikile pa cipanda.
## Mukwai abaletamba tabala tununa na amenso baishilesangafye koloboyi waba Wanderers naba Zambia, Efford Chabala, naba mubela, lilya alepilibuka bakumana nayo ilefuma mwisumbu.
## Boola yakosa kuli ba ‘Mighty’, bashala na inkongole, abantu baabo bakankamanafye abati mwandi lelo twasanga apatootwa iminang’u.
## Abalumendo babikamo umwela icakuti abaletamba, takwali kukapawila menso pantu kuti basanga impila naingila.
## Na ukumyanga umucele kashita, Oswald Chishala muli ba Wanderers ashukila impila, asesha, atala aipika umwine eka elyo ailambalika mu nshila yakwa Gerald Mungule.
## Aka kalumendo nako mano-mano kaya kalepika nga tandabube elyo kabikila Brines Mulenga, nao atonkola.
## Ala taata muleumfwakofye, boola yaishile monekafye ilyo yatanwike mwisumbu lyaba Blackpool.
## Ala nomba kaposoka, abaletamba na amashiwi yakoma kukulumba amabumba yabo pakuti yakose uleke beseebana ku fipondo fyabo.
## Boola kuti baimwena uku, kabili baisa itambila kuli ulu lubali.
## Leelo kuti cuya bonse balati impila naipwe bwangu uleke tufume amangwa iyee taata mayo eee, lilya iluluma li Simon ‘Kaodi’ Kaushi mukwai lyashukila icipapa ku lulamba lwa cibansa, awe lyakweseka nga cipembele ukulungama na ku cipanda cakwa Chabala.
## Abaletamba bamwenefye impemba yafutuka mu cipanda ninshi Chabala naba mulambalika, na ukubutuluka kwati cumbu bashula mu mbabula.
## Ba Blackpool bacimfya, boola yapwa balaimba na kaiwimbo ka kutumfya abanaabo abati
## Piiipi piiipi piipi
## Twabawina
## babo tufumo. . . babo tufumo
## nga cuula wa mainsa!
## Ata mukwai boola yabipa, ba shimaini abashaiba nangu ukubelela ukulusa icangalo, bazooka balaipantawila nafi ma jombo fyapamukoti, bakalipa abati: 
 ## “Mwenjipaishi mwe, aya malofwa teeti yatusepe, pantu tayacilya nakapwisa mukuteya.
## Kanshi bonse ba Wanderers bakateya wamupila mwalaponoka.
## “ Nacimonekafye apabuta tuutu ukuti mwalishitisha game.
## Imiteele yenu yacimoneka kwati mwalipoka amafisakanwa ku fipondo.
## Tamwa abuke akamana, lelo muleshala kuno kwine ku Kamuchanga, mwafula umuseebanya!”
## Ba kapokola balipo bwangu-bwangu ba obola abanabo ku Kamba baisa na inkoli, inkwela na impilipili pakwisa kalulula intulubundi.
Changachanga bamufunda akalaale
## Kabulo uwalebomba incito yakwensha fimasembe mumendo yapa mikoti inkongole shaku kampani shamupesha amano.
## Ena alefolafye inkaki elyo alekongola kaloba mu komboni ishakubomfya pa ng’anda.
## Kanshi imikalile yakwe pa ng ‘anda mandini yalifye iya museebanya, kwati talebomba, nifilya batila Lesa-tumba-nambo, mutima kayebele.
## Bushiku bumo imikalile yayafya ukucila mu cipimo elyo aipingwile na ukuti aye ikulika kuti ba changachanga, kusuka bamumfwilako uluse, bamupelako salary advance.
## Changachanga: Bwafya nshi ukwete ubo ulefwaila ishi ndalama ku kampani?
## Kabulo: Mukwai ine bataata nabafwa ku mushi.
## Changachanga: Nga telegramme ili kwi?
## Kabulo: Iyo mukwai bantufye abenda-mushiki ebaishile landa.
## Bashilefye elyo bashiika na ukushiika, ala pano mumwene nimfwa ku cikonko, kuti  naine wine.
## Changachanga: Icishinka apa tapali nangu ciimo, cayafya ukumwafwilisha.
## Kanshi apa icingabomba cakuti imwe muyelemba inkalata mulondolole ukulingana na ubwafya mukwete.
## Ala mukwai bapeela iciwa insambu, ishilu ili lyabwelela naku ng’anda, lyaya tuntumana na muli kalata yakabosha-mpuku aliti:
## Kuli ba changachanga,
## Mukwai nine mubomfi wenu, ishina lyandi nine Julius Kabulo Mine No. 8714.
## Incito yandi nine CAT DRIVER GRADE UG3.
## Ico nalembela uyu kalata kuli imwe nico nafilwa kuli ba Personnel Officer wenu.
## Bataata balifwa kumushi nomba naleti pamo nga ba kampani nalimo kuti mwangafwilishako indalama yakwendela, nkayafika ku cililo cabafyashi, leelo bena balikaana.
## Nomba ine ba boshi kuti nabomba shani imilimo yandi iyabu namutekenya wa katapila ilyo amatontonkanya yandi yali ku cililo ca bafyashi.
## Limbi kuti naipaya abantu nalimo kuti naipaya mashini nangu naiposa mu cilongoma. 
## Ala ba changachanga wenu ala muleumfwakoye, kanshi ama advance bapeelafye abo banwa nabo ubwalwa abali nga Kapampanta, Kosamu, Nchombolo, Ponongo na Sole-Wiliamu, 
Wiliamù, ifwe kwati tatufumya, mukuba banwenapo.
## Beene ebafwaya ukulanwa cilabuskiku ifwe fwebene ba Cuma tulelaka-lakafye ne cilaka, kutali saana.
## Nga ni Personnel munabo kuti kalekale naifuma.
## Nomba mwebakalamba bushe kanshi efyo  twakulabomba, kanofye fyonse twaisa kuli imwe?
## Bushe nangu umuntu alipena kuti abepesha wishi imfwa?
## Elyo na leave wa 7 days uwa cililo nayo balintana, nomba kuti nacita shani.

